{"tid":1544035,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"民意廣場與民憤平臺 - 古德明","createTime":"2019-09-05T11:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T12:05:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f515dbe48a23324b16445b141a037af8313efc","tid":1544035,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:56:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20190905/20762131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F20762131&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=7c687fdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E5%258F%25A4%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F20762131&h=4b6f9c2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E5%8F%A4%E5%BE%B7%E6%98%8E/daily/article/20190905/20762131</a><br />\n<br />\n民意廣場與民憤平臺 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190905/large/1567579701_4f0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190905%2Flarge%2F1567579701_4f0c.jpg&h=58c31262&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n六月二十日，香港賊婆娘鄭月娥宣布「籌建對話平臺，與不同政見者坐下來談談，盼化解紛爭」云云。現代漢語所謂「籌建對話平臺」，無非中文「準備對話」的意思，那裏真有一個什麼平臺，只是說得堂皇而己。<br />\n<br />\n鄭月娥曾託社會學者周永新研究全民退休保障，卻嫌周永新辛苦擬定的報告不合己意，冷笑一聲束諸高閣；她又曾發起「土地大辯論」，說要解決土地不足問題，卻不待「大辯論」結束，就自定傾盡公帑填海計劃。現在，港人政治上提出五大要求，她充耳不聞，卻說要「與不同政見者坐下來談談」，難怪反暴政者都嗤之以鼻，連向來左右逢源的政治學者沈旭暉都敬謝不敏，婉拒和她合演這場荒謬劇。<br />\n<br />\n而鄭月娥這邊說要聽民意，那邊一聽到市民聲音，就躲到黑警背後。所以，六月二十四日，她邀請「有心人」到官邸「籌建對話平臺」，卻把走到門前的反暴政者拒諸門外，還出動黑警把他們驅逐。她甚至連一年一度的馬季開鑼典禮都不敢如常出席，怕在場市民噓聲震天。<br />\n<br />\n而她詆為「暴徒」的以武犯禁者，八月二十五日在新城市廣場列隊走過，場內市民不但沒有噓聲，反而分立兩旁，掌聲雷動，一切見於網上錄影。這就是民意，代表至少二百萬反暴政市民，鄭月娥要聽，就到廣場去吧，何必多花公帑，聘請臨時演員出席什麼對話會。這樣的「對話平臺」只會越搞越添民憤。 <br />\n<br />\n古德明<br />\n電郵 :appledailykoo@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n這是正式錄用的香港警察嗎？ (高慧然)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n現在進行時 (楊靜)"},{"pid":"9bfe624e07432369db507bca4778e1a1f7834d65","tid":1544035,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:00:00.000Z","msg":"又po上一則下一則啲垃圾？<br />\n<br />\n你弱智？"},{"pid":"76f1e502722bcac15f5277923833c0fc0bc7ec52","tid":1544035,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:05:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵